ATTRIBUTION

Go Network Scanner is a reimagination of Angry IP Scanner
(https://angryip.org) by Anton Keks, licensed under GPLv2. This project
shares no source code with the original; all code here was written from
scratch in Go and Swift. The original Angry IP Scanner source is retained
locally in the `legacy/` directory for reference only; it is excluded from
the repository via .gitignore and is not included in distributed binaries.

Any contribution to Go Network Scanner must be original or appropriately
licensed — do not copy code from `legacy/`.
